data.title: Davis Cup - ATP World Tour - December - 2013
data.meta_description: Davis Cup - ATP World Tour - December - 2013 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document summarizes the 2014 Davis Cup World Group Final tennis tournament between Serbia and the Czech Republic. Serbia was represented by Novak Djokovic, Dusan Lajovic, Ilija Bozoljac, and Nenad Zimonjic. The Czech Republic team included Tomas Berdych, Lukas Rosol, Radek Stepanek, and Jan Hajek. The matches took place from November 21-23, 2014 at the Indoor Hard court of the Belgrade Arena in Belgrade, Serbia. The Czech Republic defeated Serbia 3-2.
